### Healthy API - Test Requests
### Usa la extensión REST Client de VS Code o copia estos requests a Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 1. REGISTRO - Crear usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Diego",
  "email": "diego@test.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "gender": "masculino",
  "weight": 75,
  "height": 175,
  "objetive": "perder peso",
  "ability": "principiante",
  "typeDiet": "vegetariana",
  "alergic": "ninguna"
}

### 2. LOGIN - Obtener token
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "diego@test.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### 3. OBTENER USUARIO ACTUAL - Requiere autenticación
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. LISTAR TODAS LAS RECETAS - Público
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes

### 5. LISTAR RECETAS FAVORITAS - Público
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/favorites

### 6. GENERAR RECETAS CON IA - Requiere autenticación + API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredients": ["pollo", "tomate", "cebolla", "ajo", "aceite de oliva"]
}

### 7. GENERAR PLAN DIARIO DE COMIDAS - Requiere autenticación + API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/dayPlan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2024-12-20",
  "userPreferences": {
    "objetive": "perder peso",
    "ability": "principiante",
    "typeDiet": "vegetariana",
    "alergic": "ninguna"
  }
}

### 8. OBTENER PLANES DEL USUARIO - Requiere autenticación
GET {{baseUrl}}/userDayPlans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8.1. OBTENER RECETAS GENERADAS POR EL USUARIO - Requiere autenticación
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/user/generated
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8.2. OBTENER RECETAS GENERADAS CON PAGINACIÓN
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/user/generated?limit=10&offset=0&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. OBTENER DETALLES DE RECETA - Público (reemplaza ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recipes/RECETA_ID_AQUI

### 10. MARCAR/DESMARCAR FAVORITO - Público (reemplaza ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/recipes/RECETA_ID_AQUI/favorite

